ster-text=\"복사되었습니다 👏\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`// In your gatsby-config.js\nplugins: [\n  {\n    resolve: \\`gatsby-transformer-remark\\`,\n    options: {\n      plugins: [\n        {\n          resolve: \\`gatsby-remark-highlight-code\\`,\n        },\n      ],\n    },\n  },\n];`, `27960695691840540000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                COPY \n              </div>\n            </div>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"javascript\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">// In your gatsby-config.js\nplugins: [\n  {\n    resolve: `gatsby-transformer-remark`,\n    options: {\n      plugins: [\n        {\n          resolve: `gatsby-remark-highlight-code`,\n        },\n      ],\n    },\n  },\n];</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<h2>index.js import 하기</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title gatsby-remark-code-title\">index.js</div>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"53289883857235450000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"복사되었습니다 👏\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`import { defineCustomElements as deckDeckGoHighlightElement } from &quot;@deckdeckgo/highlight-code/dist/loader&quot;;\ndeckDeckGoHighlightElement();`, `53289883857235450000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                COPY \n              </div>\n            </div>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"javascript\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">import { defineCustomElements as deckDeckGoHighlightElement } from &quot;@deckdeckgo/highlight-code/dist/loader&quot;;\ndeckDeckGoHighlightElement();</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>다음 옵션들을 제공해줍니다.\n저는 lineNumbers 을 활성화합니다.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>propterty</th>\n<th>type</th>\n<th>default</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>terminal</td>\n<td>carbon, ubuntu or none</td>\n<td>carbon</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>theme</td>\n<td>theme\t3024-night , a11y-dark , blackboard , base16-dark , base16-light , cobalt , dracula , duotone , hopscotch , lucario , material , monokai , night-owl , nord , oceanic-next , one-light , one-dark , panda , paraiso , seti , shades-of-purple , solarized-dark , solarized-light , synthwave , twilight , verminal , vscode , yeti , zenburn</td>\n<td>dracula</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>editable</td>\n<td>boolean</td>\n<td>false</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>lineNumbers</td>\n<td>boolean</td>\n<td>false</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title gatsby-remark-code-title\">gatsby-config.js</div>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"94924691178655250000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"복사되었습니다 👏\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`// In your gatsby-config.js\nplugins: [\n  {\n    resolve: \\`gatsby-transformer-remark\\`,\n    options: {\n      plugins: [\n        {\n          resolve: \\`gatsby-remark-highlight-code\\`,\n          options: {\n            lineNumbers: true,\n          },\n        },\n      ],\n    },\n  },\n];`, `94924691178655250000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                COPY \n              </div>\n            </div>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"javascript\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">// 